<u> <b> Knitted Rasta Hat <u/> <b/>
Yarn: #4 worsted weight
Yarn Colors: Gray for initial ribbing, Red, Yellow, Green and Black
Needles: #5 US for ribbing straight needles and circulars; #8 for hat body circular and double pointed
Begin with casting on 88 stitches using the long cast method, leaving a 3" tail
Work in K2, P2 ribbing for four rows
Switch to #5 circular needles, join ribbing making sure not to twist the ribbing and continue in 2 by 2 ribbing until piece measures 2 inches, 

